title: Steve Saka Gives Us The Full Scoop
itunes:title: Steve Saka Gives Us The Full Scoop
description: The former President of Drew Estates, Steve Saka, joins us for a scoop...as we dig into the past and the future...What happened?  Where's he going?  And other uncomfortable questions!  We light up the Eiroa Pesetas and the Cuban Stock Royal Selection.
